Molloy et al. v. Board of Health. (Supreme Court, General Term, Second Department. December, 1891.) Action by William Y. Molloy and Frank W. Molloy against the board of health of the town of Mamaroneek.

Argued before Barnard, P. J., and Pratt, J.

Ho opinion. Motion denied. See 15 N. Y. Supp. 487.
